      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm putting together some personalized training programs for a new group of clients at my gym. I want to be as scientific as possible with the programming. Are there any actual biological differences in things like muscle fiber composition or overall athletic potential between different racial groups that I should keep in mind to get the best results for them?",
