      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"well-known fact\"? That sounds pretty definitive. Do you have any specific studies or citations that back up those claims about Africans having more slow-twitch fibers or the differences in East/South Asian capacities? I want to make sure I'm not just following outdated tropes if I'm going to use this for professional programming.",
